\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我今晚試吓先，<br />\n唔該絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96f37a943290c58015e9f66d7f7f9f69fd148158","tid":167290,"uid":13555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T03:57:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/23/115739_6b608e079350c90ac2f729a6fd869d19.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F23%2F115739_6b608e079350c90ac2f729a6fd869d19.jpg&h=62f26770&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n依個 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05d9c8f8a0d6877631cc5de6d62aec84058da871","tid":167290,"uid":2022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T03:58:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0559b04860632c5c6e74bafe52b10f3121a35ee1","tid":167290,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T04:17:41.000Z","msg":"留名等巴打教路係咩膚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"274e7936a0d34c3083a8c127dccae85665ea400c","tid":167290,"uid":91025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T04:21:22.000Z","msg":"凹洞都得？"},{"pid":"00a34d5b4fe4ecebf015675d9f62fc694cc49fad","tid":167290,"uid":500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T04:41:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>凹洞都得？</blockquote><br />\n凹洞要激光"},{"pid":"c51b26e971ae11c9adf54a4ff3236d37fb65e786","tid":167290,"uid":78534,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T04:47:30.000Z","msg":"一個二個俾人講兩句就以為神藥咁 屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢支野有藥性同致