ji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同埋要幾錢嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe0845c7c0cb31f7e5408eb5138fe8516cab5fc7","tid":167290,"uid":6762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T15:44:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>join 過好多course 乜撚野鑽石，冰極，激光，co2都做過<br />\n夾埋洗左五皮野都唔係好見效，做完又生由留印<br />\n最後買支娥羅納英搞掂左，印都冇埋<br />\n仆佢個街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n娥羅納英去到印同平暗瘡？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n臨訓洗完面搽上去<br />\n石頭瘡暗瘡白頭粉刺都掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n石頭瘡真係搞唔掂既話，用雲南白藥膏剪細細塊貼上去<br />\n印可以沖涼嗰陣撻少少豆腐上去敷下<br />\n依家塊面真係滑過豆腐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n雲南白藥膏 係邊一隻貼?"},{"pid":"2909ea42c47f0f49ea4399e571b038da94b7fe9b","tid":167290,"uid":38820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T15:59:10.000Z","msg":"做 laser 真係要換皮膚專科，貴就貴d,有保證"},{"pid":"357c24630f869f6142a73bd977deed8287caab53","tid":167290,"uid":94929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T08:19:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>激光有無介紹講下？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同問，好想去啲凹凸洞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n暫時最有效好似係fractional co2 laser 無咁嚴重就restore 嚴重就repair</blockquote><br />\nCO2有冇邊間推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ado